{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id6ba688d3-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1262"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1262"},"text":"§ 1262.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions and authorizations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id6ba688d4-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1262/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" As used in sections 1259 through 1262 of this title—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id6ba688d5-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1262/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “institution of higher education” means an educational institution described in the first sentence of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1001"},"text":"section 1001 of title 20","children":[],"tail":" (other than an institution of any agency of the United States) which is accredited by a nationally recognized accrediting agency or association approved by the Administrator for this purpose. For purposes of this subsection, the Administrator shall publish a list of nationally recognized accrediting agencies or associations which he determines to be reliable authority as to the quality of training offered."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id6ba688d6-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1262/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “academic year” means an academic year or its equivalent, as determined by the Administrator.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id6ba688d7-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1262/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Administrator shall annually report his activities under sections 1259 through 1262 of this title, including recommendations for needed revisions in the provisions thereof.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id6ba688d8-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s1262/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" There are authorized to be appropriated $25,000,000 per fiscal year for the fiscal years ending ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1973","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1974","children":[],"tail":", and "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1975","children":[],"tail":", $6,000,000 for the fiscal year ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1977-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1977","children":[],"tail":", $7,000,000 for the fiscal year ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1978","children":[],"tail":", $7,000,000 for the fiscal year ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1979-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1979","children":[],"tail":", $7,000,000 for the fiscal year ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1980","children":[],"tail":", $7,000,000 for the fiscal year ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1981","children":[],"tail":", $7,000,000 for the fiscal year ending "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-09-30"},"text":"September 30, 1982","children":[],"tail":", such sums as may be necessary for fiscal years 1983 through 1985, and $7,000,000 